How can I get incentive ad credit?

To become eligible for ad credit, your account must complete and pass business verification, and accumulate over $5,000 in spend. Additionally, you'll need to establish a relationship with an Account Manager (AM), who can then request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
